  "detailed_description": "In this mix of farming simulator and spaceship shooter, you control Little Eden, an independent Farm Ship fending for herself and its precious resources while flying through the skies of the Soaring Plains. Destroy planetoids, collect seeds to plant, craft ammunition and fight for survival against the terrible Pirate Coalition.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Explore and collect resources</h2>Explore the different biomes, harvest the planetoids and gather resources to help your adventure.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2524720/extras/9d3dad27cadf74d8e1a2a24a97d0f472.poster.avif?t=1761567382\" width=598 height=114 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2524720/extras/9d3dad27cadf74d8e1a2a24a97d0f472.webm?t=1761567382\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2524720/extras/9d3dad27cadf74d8e1a2a24a97d0f472.mp4?t=1761567382\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Plant and Harvest unique seeds</h2>From the hardy Iron Nut to the unstable Dragon Toadstool, you plant your own ammunition in Little Eden.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2524720/extras/701ad0d5feb586633b9b1323534fd6db.poster.avif?t=1761567382\" width=598 height=114 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2524720/extras/701ad0d5feb586633b9b1323534fd6db.webm?t=1761567382\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2524720/extras/701ad0d5feb586633b9b1323534fd6db.mp4?t=1761567382\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Use Powerful Guns</h2>Be it a machine gun, laser or grenades, make your enemies regret ever crossing your piece of sky.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2524720/extras/2b8b23b4e98fd9bc1fe0c44f80c19fe2.poster.avif?t=1761567382\" width=598 height=114 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2524720/extras/2b8b23b4e98fd9bc1fe0c44f80c19fe2.webm?t=1761567382\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2524720/extras/2b8b23b4e98fd9bc1fe0c44f80c19fe2.mp4?t=1761567382\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Beware the pirates!</h2>Little Eden’s Soaring Plains are populated by terrible pirates, be careful while exploring, engaging in combat with pirates might be lethal. Are you pilot enough to survive such encounters?<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2524720/extras/b8609fa3daa7efce423cf1f1c5877e89.poster.avif?t=1761567382\" width=598 height=114 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2524720/extras/b8609fa3daa7efce423cf1f1c5877e89.webm?t=1761567382\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2524720/extras/b8609fa3daa7efce423cf1f1c5877e89.mp4?t=1761567382\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Conquer Upgrades</h2>By exploring enough you will find improvements for Little Eden. Upgrade your guns, defenses and maneuverability and seek new heights.",
  "about_the_game": "In this mix of farming simulator and spaceship shooter, you control Little Eden, an independent Farm Ship fending for herself and its precious resources while flying through the skies of the Soaring Plains. Destroy planetoids, collect seeds to plant, craft ammunition and fight for survival against the terrible Pirate Coalition.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Explore and collect resources</h2>Explore the different biomes, harvest the planetoids and gather resources to help your adventure.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2524720/extras/9d3dad27cadf74d8e1a2a24a97d0f472.poster.avif?t=1761567382\" width=598 height=114 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2524720/extras/9d3dad27cadf74d8e1a2a24a97d0f472.webm?t=1761567382\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2524720/extras/9d3dad27cadf74d8e1a2a24a97d0f472.mp4?t=1761567382\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Plant and Harvest unique seeds</h2>From the hardy Iron Nut to the unstable Dragon Toadstool, you plant your own ammunition in Little Eden.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2524720/extras/701ad0d5feb586633b9b1323534fd6db.poster.avif?t=1761567382\" width=598 height=114 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2524720/extras/701ad0d5feb586633b9b1323534fd6db.webm?t=1761567382\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2524720/extras/701ad0d5feb586633b9b1323534fd6db.mp4?t=1761567382\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Use Powerful Guns</h2>Be it a machine gun, laser or grenades, make your enemies regret ever crossing your piece of sky.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2524720/extras/2b8b23b4e98fd9bc1fe0c44f80c19fe2.poster.avif?t=1761567382\" width=598 height=114 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2524720/extras/2b8b23b4e98fd9bc1fe0c44f80c19fe2.webm?t=1761567382\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2524720/extras/2b8b23b4e98fd9bc1fe0c44f80c19fe2.mp4?t=1761567382\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Beware the pirates!</h2>Little Eden’s Soaring Plains are populated by terrible pirates, be careful while exploring, engaging in combat with pirates might be lethal. Are you pilot enough to survive such encounters?<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2524720/extras/b8609fa3daa7efce423cf1f1c5877e89.poster.avif?t=1761567382\" width=598 height=114 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2524720/extras/b8609fa3daa7efce423cf1f1c5877e89.webm?t=1761567382\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2524720/extras/b8609fa3daa7efce423cf1f1c5877e89.mp4?t=1761567382\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Conquer Upgrades</h2>By exploring enough you will find improvements for Little Eden. Upgrade your guns, defenses and maneuverability and seek new heights.",
